[[File:Playa-de-monsul.jpg|right|thumb|400px|{{PAGENAME}} .]]''' Â-ngì-mòi-lî-â-sén ''' ({{lang-es|Provincia de Almería}}) he [[Sî-pân-ngà]] nàm-phu ke yit-ke [[Sî-pân-ngà Hàng-chṳn-khî va̍k | sén-fun]], vi-yî [[Ôn-tha̍t-lû-sî-â | Ôn-tha̍t-lû-sî-â Chhṳ-chhṳ-khî]] ke tûng-phu. Kì ke si-chû yû [[Kak-là-na̍p-tha̍t-sén]], [[Mu̍k-ngì-sî-â-sén]], yî-khi̍p [[Thi-chûng-hói]]. Sú-fú vì [[Â-ngì-mòi-lî-â]]. 
Â-ngì-mòi-lî-â-sén thú-thi mien-chit vì 8,769 km², ngìn-khiéu yû 546,499 (2002-ngièn), chúng-khiung yû 101 ke Chhṳ-chhṳ-sṳ. 

